{"pageProps":{"id":["lang","go","basic","var.adoc"],"postInfo":{"type":"adoc","doc":{"title":"Go: 变量","author":"weily","tags":[],"version":"1.0","date":1590336000000,"content":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_声明变量\">声明变量</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_声明并初始化变量\">声明并初始化变量</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_短变量声明\">短变量声明</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_常量\">常量</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_iota\"><code>iota</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_声明变量\">声明变量</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在 Go 语言中，用 <code>var</code> 关键字声明一组变量。和函数参数列表类似，类型放在变量名之后。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> c, python, java <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">bool</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_声明并初始化变量\">声明并初始化变量</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>用 <code>var</code> 声明变量时，可以带有初始值。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> i, j <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>如果初始值存在，则可以省略类型，变量会使用初始值的类型。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> c, python, java = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"no!\"</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_短变量声明\">短变量声明</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在函数内部，可以用操作符 <code>:=</code> 来替代 <code>var</code> 声明一个具有隐式类型的变量。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">penta</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(v <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span>)</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">int</span></span> {\n\tfactor := <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> factor * v\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在函数外部，因为每一个语句必须以关键字开头，所以还是老老实实用 <code>var</code> 吧。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>可以使用操作符 <code>:=</code> 同时定义几个变量。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">a, b := <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>操作符 <code>:=</code> 左边不一定都是新变量，只要至少有一个新变量即可。比如下例，变量 <code>c</code> 最终的值是 9：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">b, c := <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\nc, d := <span class=\"hljs-number\">9</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_常量\">常量</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>声明常量就像是声明变量那样，不过要用 <code>const</code> 关键字，而不是用 <code>var</code>。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int64</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>像变量那样，可以在一行内定义多个常量：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> b, c = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>如果同时要定义好几个常量，单行些比较长的话，还可以用下面的带括号的常量声明语法来定义多个常量：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> (\n\td = <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n\te = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>不可以使用 <code>:=</code> 语法来声明常量。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>目前，只有以下几种常量：布尔、<code>rune</code>、整数、浮点数、复数和字符串。不支持创建自定义类型的常量。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>常量声明中的表达式可以省略（除了第一行之外），被省略的表达式实际是重复上一行的表达式。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> (\n\ta = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 第一行不可省略</span>\n\tb     <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 这一行省略了常量表达式，重复上一行，所以 b 的值也是 1</span>\n\tc     <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 这一行省略了常量表达式，重复上一行，上一行也省略了，往上找到第一行，所以 c 的值也是 1</span>\n)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_iota\"><code>iota</code></h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在常量声明中，可以使用预定义的标识符 <code>iota</code> 来表示连续的无类型整数常量。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> a = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// a 的值是 0</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> b = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// b 的值也是 0</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>上面的例子里，<code>a</code> 和 <code>b</code> 的值都是 0，有啥意思呢？确实没啥意思，<code>iota</code> 要用带括号的常量声明语法才能显示出威力。比如下例：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> (\n\tSunday = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 0</span>\n\tMonday        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 1</span>\n\tTuesday       <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 2</span>\n\tWednesday     <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 3</span>\n\tThursday      <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 4</span>\n\tFriday        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 5</span>\n\tPartyday      <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 6</span>\n\tnumberOfDays  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 7</span>\n)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这个例子中，<code>Sunday</code> 以下的常量表达式都使用 <code>iota</code>，但是他们的值不同。因为 <code>iota</code> 的取值是\n<a href=\"https://golang.org/ref/spec#Iota\">括号中常量出现的行数</a>（从 0 开始，注释行不算），\n所以 <code>Sunday</code> 是第“0”个，所以其值为 0，<code>Monday</code> 是第“1”个，所以其值为 1，依次往后推。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>再比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> (\n\ta, b = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// a == 0, b == 0 (iota == 0)</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// some comments       // 注释行忽略</span>\n\tc, _                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// c == 1         (iota == 1)</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 注意，这里必须写成 “c, _”，而不是单独一个 “c”</span>\n\td, e                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// d == 2, e == 6 (iota == 2)</span>\n)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>还可以对 <code>iota</code> 做运算。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> (\n\ta = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span>     <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// a == 0  (iota == 0)</span>\n\t_            <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 忽略     (iota == 1)</span>\n\tc            <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// c == 2  (iota == 2)</span>\n\td = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">iota</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// d == 9  (iota == 3)</span>\n\te            <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// e == 12 (iota == 4)</span>\n)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"},"toc":{"type":"simple","title":"Go 语言基础","description":"这里是 Go 语言 XXXXXX","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"basic.adoc"},{"title":"函数","path":"func.adoc"},{"title":"变量","path":"var.adoc"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"basic-types.adoc"},{"title":"字符串","path":"string.adoc"},{"title":"指针","path":"ptr.adoc"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"array-slice.adoc"},{"title":"映射","path":"map.adoc"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"struct.adoc"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"itf.adoc"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"type.adoc"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"for.adoc"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"if.adoc"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"switch.adoc"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"defer.adoc"},{"title":"并发","path":"concurrency.adoc"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"pkg-import.adoc"}]}}},"__N_SSG":true}